{"tid":2097521,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁子超：不能絶對排除或經接觸食肆碗碟感染病毒","createTime":"2020-07-07T01:50:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T03:13:54.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"57d20e040b46213f328d4af0a2be8424bad9a0e4","tid":2097521,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T01:50:47.000Z","msg":"梁子超：不能絶對排除或經接觸食肆碗碟感染病毒<br />\n2020-07-07 HKT 09:27<br />\n<br />\n&quot;醫學會傳染病顧問委員會主席梁子超，接受本台節目《千禧年代》訪問時表示，雖然食肆顧客未必會與廚師有直接接觸，但廚師會與食肆接待員有接觸，有機會將病毒傳播開去。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;不能絶對排除經接觸食肆碗碟而感染的機會率，但經人與人接觸傳播的風險最大。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536213-20200707.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536213-20200707.htm&d=uYDAXyhVPN7xTSuHIXBXEhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=373002aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536213-20200707.htm&h=c3954073\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536213-20200707.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>不過我都會照常出外用膳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"257973443d7c5c851e56af844e1123b82128cc06","tid":2097521,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T02:47:19.000Z","msg":"叫外賣喇，港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bf85d4e912c0396324dc32336f38f68d0e44d1","tid":2097521,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T03:08:21.000Z","msg":"快啲停返食肆坐人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45579192e41eb95f7c2ad52b2da1c5021ac9673","tid":2097521,"uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T03:09:32.000Z","msg":"外賣自取優惠又番返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj